    "4.2.4 Suffixes learned from a single (Q, R) against a source LLM can transfer to other LLMs.",
    "Following Eq.",
    "(8), we exam the cross-LLM transferability of the learned suffixes.",
    "The results are presented in Table 4 and Fig. 21 (See App.H.6 for more discussions).",
